<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Git on NavyD的个人博客</title><link>/tags/git/</link><description>Recent content in Git on NavyD的个人博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 23:55:08 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/git/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>CI Practice</title><link>/posts/2025/02/ci-practice/</link><pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 14:04:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/2025/02/ci-practice/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="git-hook-manager">git hook manager
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/evilmartians/lefthook"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>evilmartians/lefthook: Fast and powerful Git hooks manager for any type of projects&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>pre-commit/pre-commit: A framework for managing and maintaining multi-language pre-commit hooks&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://xfyuan.github.io/2024/06/five-cool-and-surprising-ways-to-configure-lefthook-for-automation-joy/"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Lefthook 的五种武器&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://evilmartians.com/chronicles/5-cool-and-surprising-ways-to-configure-lefthook-for-automation-joy"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>5 cool (and surprising) ways to configure Lefthook for automation joy&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="lefthook">lefthook
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="并行">并行
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>在 pre-commit 时通常会存在检查与修复操作，一个问题，并行处理同一个文件且都尝试更新时，如何处理竞争条件。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>配置
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/parallel.html#parallel"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>parallel&lt;/a>
可以让
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/Commands.html#commands"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>&lt;code>commands&lt;/code>&lt;/a>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/Scripts.html#scripts"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Scripts&lt;/a>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/jobs.html#jobs"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>&lt;code>jobs&lt;/code>&lt;/a>
类型的任务并行，但有时对其中某些特定的任务是需要先后顺序的，如所有的 lint 可以并行，但 fixed 通常需要在 lint 后执行避免竞争&lt;/p>
&lt;h5 id="jobs">jobs
&lt;/h5>&lt;p>参考
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/jobs.html#differences-from-commands-and-scripts"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Differences from Commands and Scripts&lt;/a>
提供了 job 组的概念，分组后 jobs 并行串行可组合方便&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="run-with-shell">run with shell
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>在运行命令
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/run.html"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>&lt;code>run: command list&lt;/code>&lt;/a>
时无法指定 shell，&lt;code>*nix&lt;/code>, &lt;code>windows&lt;/code> 不兼容语法，只能使用
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/Scripts.html"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>scripts&lt;/a>
文件执行，对于某些简单的命令非常不方便。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如检查文件名在 windows 上是否合法参考
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit-hooks/issues/589"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
># Add check for illegal Windows filenames&lt;/a>
使用 &lt;code>(?i)((^|/)(CON|PRN|AUX|NUL|COM[\d¹²³]|LPT[\d¹²³])(\.|/|$)|[&amp;lt;&amp;gt;:\&amp;quot;\\|?*\x00-\x1F]|/[^/]*[\.\s]/|[^/]*[\.\s]$)&lt;/code> 正则检查时需要创建文件而不能在 yaml 文件中写简单 python 的代码。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>另外，在 &lt;code>run: command to {staged_files}&lt;/code> 看起来也非常不稳定，使用
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://lefthook.dev/configuration/run.html#quotes"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>quotes&lt;/a>
处理模板，可能存在转义的问题&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/evilmartians/lefthook/issues/953"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
># Wrap commands in Git bash on Windows&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/evilmartians/lefthook/issues/786"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
># Invalid escaping of {staged_files}&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="lint">lint
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="yaml">yaml
&lt;/h3>&lt;h4 id="schema">schema
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>在
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://www.schemastore.org/json/"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>JSON Schema Store&lt;/a>
中提供了 schema 结构以方便检查&lt;/p>
&lt;p>yamllint 不支持验证
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/adrienverge/yamllint/issues/37"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Support to validate against a schema&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/redhat-developer/yaml-language-server"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>redhat-developer/yaml-language-server&lt;/a>
虽然支持验证
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/redhat-developer/yaml-language-server#using-inlined-schema"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Using inlined schema&lt;/a>
如 &lt;code># yaml-language-server: $schema=&amp;lt;urlToTheSchema&amp;gt;&lt;/code> ，但未提供 cli 接口运行
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/redhat-developer/yaml-language-server/issues/535"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>Command Line API/Option&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3971822/how-do-i-validate-my-yaml-file-from-command-line"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>How do I validate my YAML file from command line?&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="git-commit-message">git commit message
&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/conventional-changelog/commitlint"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>conventional-changelog/commitlint: Lint commit messages&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/commitizen-tools/commitizen"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>commitizen-tools/commitizen: Create committing rules for projects 🚀 auto bump versions ⬆️ and auto changelog generation&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>注意：对于非 js 项目 &lt;code>npm install --save-dev @commitlint/config-conventional @commitlint/cli&lt;/code> 是无法使用的&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Merge Two Git Repos</title><link>/posts/2021/08/merge-two-git-repos/</link><pubDate>Sun, 08 Aug 2021 01:49:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/2021/08/merge-two-git-repos/</guid><description>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/merge-two-git-repos/2021-08-08-01-49-49.png" alt="Featured image of post Merge Two Git Repos" />&lt;h2 id="问题">问题
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>从原始博客仓库&lt;code>blog-resources&lt;/code>中迁移所有记录到新的hugo博客仓库&lt;code>navyd.github.io&lt;/code>新文件夹下&lt;code>content/res&lt;/code>中，以后慢慢修改为hugo博客形式。下面是两个仓库的目录结构&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code>../
- blog-resources/
- .git/
- blog.md
- ...
- navyd.github.io/
- .git/
- content/
- post/
- ...
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;h2 id="分析">分析
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://stackoverflow.com/a/10548919/8566831"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>git merge&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>cd navyd.github.io
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git checkout -b blog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git remote add blog-res ../blog-resources
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git fetch blog-res --tags
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git merge --allow-unrelated-histories blog-res/master &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># or whichever branch you want to merge&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git remote remove blog-res
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>mv test.md content/res &lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 移动之前仓库的文件到res中&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git commit -m &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;mv to res folder&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>这个方法有个很大的缺点，在merge时会合并到根目录，可能出现冲突，无法自定义合并到子文件夹中，虽然可以提前使用
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://github.com/newren/git-filter-repo"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>git-filter-repo&lt;/a>
命令：&lt;code>git filter-repo --to-subdirectory-filter blog-res&lt;/code>，但是&lt;code>ubuntu 20.04&lt;/code>无法安装，放弃使用merge的方法&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="/posts/2021/08/merge-two-git-repos/2021-08-08-01-49-49.png"
width="1151"
height="976"
srcset="/posts/2021/08/merge-two-git-repos/2021-08-08-01-49-49_hu_78c16fe54202030a.png 480w, /posts/2021/08/merge-two-git-repos/2021-08-08-01-49-49_hu_e84ae8aea62cdedc.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="117"
data-flex-basis="283px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="注意">注意
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>如果仓库中存在未被git管理的文件，一定要备份好，&lt;code>git reset --hard&lt;/code>将会完全覆盖这样的文件，无法找回&lt;/p>
&lt;p>使用&lt;code>git reset --hard &amp;lt;commit_id&amp;gt;&lt;/code>回到合并前的状态。如果操作失误出现大量的&lt;code>untracked files&lt;/code>，可以使用&lt;code>git clean&lt;/code>删除&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 查看可被清除的文件&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git clean -n
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 删除文件目录&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git clean -f -d
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果在merge后想要撤消，但是使用&lt;code>git log&lt;/code>找不能合并的记录日志对应的commit id，可以使用&lt;code>git reflog&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ git log
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>commit 0504c8037617b01b6c90183a7b8fcdaf71216411 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>HEAD -&amp;gt; main, blog&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Merge: a30ea67 34cef1f
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Author: navyd &amp;lt;dhjnavyd@gmail.com&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Date: Sun Aug &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">8&lt;/span> 01:39:45 &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2021&lt;/span> +0800
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> Add &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;content/res/&amp;#39;&lt;/span> from commit &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;34cef1f6fe6477181818e55ff468e9a62c7fccbf&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> git-subtree-dir: content/res
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> git-subtree-mainline: a30ea67efb72183d0d696dc74d9677a98b784035
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> git-subtree-split: 34cef1f6fe6477181818e55ff468e9a62c7fccbf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>commit a30ea67efb72183d0d696dc74d9677a98b784035 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Author: navyd &amp;lt;dhjnavyd@gmail.com&amp;gt;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Date: Sat Aug &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">7&lt;/span> 00:26:58 &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">2021&lt;/span> +0800
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> even主题问题
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ git reflog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>0504c80 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>HEAD -&amp;gt; main, blog&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>0&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: merge blog: Fast-forward
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>1&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to a30ea67
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>c9dc62b HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>2&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to HEAD~1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>e341955 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>3&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: checkout: moving from blog to main
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>0504c80 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>HEAD -&amp;gt; main, blog&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>4&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to 0504c80
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>94302ef HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>5&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: commit: test
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>0504c80 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>HEAD -&amp;gt; main, blog&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>6&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to 0504c8037617b01b6c90183a7b8fcdaf71216411
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>7&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to a30ea67
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>00dc6b8 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>8&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: commit: mv
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>1f736a4 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>9&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to 1f736a4272dbd8306d8451bcb9fe5d35ce81878e
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>10&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: checkout: moving from main to blog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>e341955 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>11&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: merge blog: Fast-forward
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>12&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: checkout: moving from blog to main
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>e341955 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>13&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: commit: remove index.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>c9dc62b HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>14&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: commit: mv to old folder
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>e965a30 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>15&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: merge blog-res/master: Merge made by the &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;recursive&amp;#39;&lt;/span> strategy.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>16&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to a30ea67
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>17&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: reset: moving to HEAD~
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>e440e06 HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>18&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: merge blog-res/master: Merge made by the &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;recursive&amp;#39;&lt;/span> strategy.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>a30ea67 &lt;span style="color:#f92672">(&lt;/span>origin/main, origin/HEAD&lt;span style="color:#f92672">)&lt;/span> HEAD@&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>19&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>: checkout: moving from main to blog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ git reset --hard id
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="解决">解决
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>在这里提到
&lt;a
class="link"
href="https://stackoverflow.com/a/14992078/8566831"
target="_blank"
rel="noopener"
>使用git subtree&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>cd navyd.github.io
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git checkout -b blog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 添加blog-resources@master&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git subtree add --prefix&lt;span style="color:#f92672">=&lt;/span>content/res ../blog-resources master
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#75715e"># 合并blog到main分支&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git checkout main
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>git merge blog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>完成合并log&lt;/p>
